{"content":"<h2 id=\"_89-按位与按位或运算符\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#_89-按位与按位或运算符\"><span>89.按位与按位或运算符</span></a></h2>\n<p><strong>&amp;(按位与)</strong>：参加运算的两个数据，如果相应的二进制都为1，则该结果为1，否则为0</p>\n<p><strong>|(按位或)</strong>：参加运算的两个数据，如果相应的二进制都为0，则该位结果都为0，否则为1</p>\n<h2 id=\"_90-按位异或\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#_90-按位异或\"><span>90.按位异或</span></a></h2>\n<div class=\"hint-container info\">\n<p class=\"hint-container-title\">相关信息</p>\n<p>按位异或也称为XOF运算符，如果相应的二进制位不同，则该位结果为1，否则为0</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"language-c line-numbers-mode\" data-ext=\"c\" data-title=\"c\"><button class=\"copy\" title=\"复制代码\" data-copied=\"已复制\"></button><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">#</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">include</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\"> &#x3C;</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">stdio.h</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">void</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> jh</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">void</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">)</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">                //交换两个变量的值，不使用中间变量</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">\tint</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> a </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4